Гаряча вакансія
Customer Care Expert (English)
WIX
IT;
50–250 співробітників
Київ, вулиця Паньківська, 14А.
1,8 км від центру ·
На мапі
Повна зайнятість.
Опис вакансії
We are:Wix’s amazing Customer Care team in Kyiv. We use our unique understanding of Wix products to provide support and inspiration to over 150 million users around the world!We offer competitive pay, great benefits, including time off, health insurance, subsidized lunch, happy hours and so much more. You’ll find a relaxed and friendly atmosphere, your coworkers (and bosses) fantastic and a lot of opportunities for growth in this fast-paced, high profile startup environment.We work in small teams to allow everyone to express their creativity and we never stop learning.You are:Proficient in written and spoken English, and eager to explore new technology. You have the ability to learn new concepts and solve problems thoughtfully and effectively. You have customer service experience in any industry, strong critical thinking skills, you know how to identify challenges and solutions. You love to help other people and want to influence the way our users perceive our products. You are comfortable working in a fast-paced and deadline-driven environment. No tech experience is required, we’ll train you!As a Customer Care Expert, you will:Provide Wix users with technical solutions over the e-mail and in proactive and reactive chat.Analyze user behavior, content suitability, develop and maintain positive customer relations and satisfaction.Influence the way we support our users and improve it to make sure our users' experience is the best possible.Work with all other departments and product teams, and liaise with them about our users' needs.You embrace the challenges of global communication and love working as part of a team. You take ownership of every project you touch and always take initiative.Please send your CV in English.
